\c 31
\s Egipita haingabatsiri, asi Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Vane nhamo vanoburukira Egipita kundotsvaka kubatsirwa, vanotenda mabhiza, vanovimba nengoro dzokurwa nokuti izhinji, uye navatasvi vamabhiza nokuti vane simba kwazvo, asi havatariri kuno Mutsvene waIsraeri, kana kutsvaka Jehovha.
\v 2 Kunyange zvakadaro naiye akachenjera, achauisa nhamo, haangadzosi mashoko ake, asi achamukira imba yavanoita zvakaipa, navanobatsirana navanoita zvakaipa.
\v 3 Zvino VaEgipita vanhu, havazi Mwari, namabhiza avo inyama, haasi mweya; zvino kana Jehovha achitandavadza ruoko rwake, anobatsira achagumburwa nowanobatsirwa achawira pasi, vese vachapera pamwe chete.
\p
\v 4 Nokuti zvanzi naJehovha kwandiri: Zvakaita seshumba nomwana weshumba zvinoombera chayabata; kunyange vafudzi vazhinji vakakokerwa kuzorwa nayo, haingavhunduswi namanzwi avo; haingavi nehanya nokupopota kwavo; saizvozvo Jehovha wehondo achaburukira pamusoro pegomo reZiyoni napamusoro pechikomo charo kuzorwa navo.
\v 5 Seshiri dzinodzengerera, saizvozvo Jehovha achatavirira Jerusarema; acharitavirira nokurirwira, acharidarika nokurisunungura.
\p
\v 6 Dzokerai kuna iye wamakamukira zvikuru, imwi vana vaIsraeri.
\v 7 Nokuti nezuva iro umwe neumwe ucharasi a zvifananidzo zvake zvesirivha nezvifananidzo zvake zvegoridhe, zvamakazviitira namaoko enyu, zvikava zvivi kwamuri.
\p
\v 8 Ipapo muAsiriya achawa nomunondo usati uri womunhu; munondo usati uri wavanhu uchamudya; achatiza pamberi pomunondo, namajaya ake achabatirwa chibharo.
\v 9 Dombo rake richatiza nokutya, machinda ake achavhunduswa nomureza, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, anomoto wake paZiyoni, nechoto chake paJerusarema.